Package: gcceii
Title: GCC Economic Integration Index
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("GCC-Stat", "Economic Statistics Department",
           email = "stats@gccstat.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Kari", "Manninen", role = "aut")
    )
Description: R package for calculating the GCC Economic Integration Index
    (GCCEII) using the COINr framework for composite indicator construction.
    The index measures economic integration across the six Gulf Cooperation
    Council countries (UAE, Bahrain, Saudi Arabia, Oman, Qatar, Kuwait) from
    2015-2023. It covers six dimensions: Trade Integration, Financial
    Integration, Labor & Mobility, Infrastructure, Sustainability, and
    Convergence.
